| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1327 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8accfd68-bc83-5851-97c5-cc4dc55d40cf"
